@startmindmap
* BizConsult
** Account & Access
*** Sign up / Log in / Log out
*** Role selection (Customer / Consultant / Admin)
*** Profile management (Customer, Consultant)
** Public Discovery
*** Public site (home/services/about)
*** Public consultants directory & search
** Customer Functions
*** Browse consultants & view ratings
*** Request consultation (≥24h lead time)
*** Manage consultations (view/edit/cancel/respond to proposal)
*** View/download reports
*** Rate consultant
*** Messaging per consultation
*** View notifications
** Consultant Functions
*** Profile creation/update (resume, expertise, etc.)
*** Consultation inbox (view/accept/reject/propose/complete)
*** Scheduling & meeting link generation
*** Create/save/view consultation report
*** Rate customer (if enabled)
*** Messaging per consultation
*** View notifications
** Admin Functions
*** Manage users (view/suspend customers)
*** Manage consultants (approve/reject/suspend/unsuspend; approve updates)
*** Manage consultations (search/filter/list; view details)
*** Reports (view/export PDF/Excel/CSV)
*** View ratings (consultant→customer, customer→consultant via profiles)
*** Notifications (follow links)
** Ratings & Feedback
*** Customer→Consultant ratings
*** Consultant→Customer ratings (admin viewable)
** Messaging
*** Consultation messages (customer–consultant)
** Notifications
*** Consultation and system notifications
** Reporting & Exports
*** Admin reports dashboard
*** Exports (PDF, Excel, CSV)
@endmindmap

